Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:37.80,OP,,0,0,0,,The rain stops, there's a break in the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.76,OP,,0,0,0,,The blue sky's calling out to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:45.14,OP,,0,0,0,,Alright, it's almost time to head out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:48.48,OP,,0,0,0,,I don't need anyone else's advice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:51.40,OP,,0,0,0,,I've gotta trust my own instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:56.45,OP,,0,0,0,,It's high time I found my own way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:58.66,OP,,0,0,0,,Fire Up, Ignition
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:01.33,OP,,0,0,0,,The heavy pressure's on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:03.58,OP,,0,0,0,,Slam the accelerator and power through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:08.75,OP,,0,0,0,,Surprise, the whole world's got drive!\N{\fs30}(It's faster than ever)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:13.92,OP,,0,0,0,,Feeling high like you're finally awake\N{\fs30}(Show me your Drivin')
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:19.47,OP,,0,0,0,,Once you're on the road to destiny\N{\fs30}(Keep chasin' forever)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:24.14,OP,,0,0,0,,There's no way to go in reverse...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:26.89,OP,,0,0,0,,All we need is Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:35.99,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(482,478)\4a00\fs56\shad3\bord1.6\pos(640,460)}One Day in April, 2015
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about this for a while now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How exactly did the Special Crimes Unit assemble this wacky cast of characters? {liberties}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's rather simple. We're all involved with Kamen Rider, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I get why everybody here is on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You were rescued by a Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rinna knew Krim before he died, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, aside from Shin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't just gloss over my part!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:07.55,Default Top,,0,0,0,,What I'm asking is what's the deal with Kyu and old man Otta? {no comma after "what I'm asking is" since the whole thing is informal grammar to begin with.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:10.98,EpTitle,,0,0,0,,{\fad(398,478)\an1\move(1189,620,350,620,23,398)\fs42}Episode 1{\c&H5B42D3&\3c&HDAE3E6&}   How{\c\3c\be1} was the Special Crimes Unit assembled?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:09.70,Default Top,,0,0,0,,They've got no connection to Kamen Rider, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:11.72,Default Top,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a little story, Krim? {liberties}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need to look into a murder from one year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here's the outline of the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,April 4th, 2014.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Odagiri Masahiko of Shinkyo University's human sciences department mysteriously died. {DAMN that's a mouthful.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death was between 7 and 9pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no sign of a struggle, the cause of death was recorded as cardiac arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But the professor's assistant, Kasai Hitomi, went missing around that time...{But for some reason, the assistant of another professor, Kasai Hitomi, went missing.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, that date...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that the day of the Global Freeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:03:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what does this have to do\Nwith the Special Crimes Unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand if you can solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun. I'll solve it at mach speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're showing your negative traits, Gou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Shinnosuke? It will look bad if a detective gets one upped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we race to see who can figure it out first, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gou! Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, don't turn this into one of your weird competitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you should be interested too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If this case really does involve Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Krim is probably hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should do a little investigating of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you did try to transform into Kamen Rider once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}DRIVE: TYPE SPEED!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that I'll need to find another candidate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off to do some investigating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Mr. Kusakabe Akira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.61,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(232,230)\pos(555,490)\fs34\bord1.6\shad1.4\4c&H000000&\4a&H00&}Metro Police Public Safety Detective \N {\fs52\shad3}Kusakabe Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:57.89,Default Top,,0,0,0,,That's right... {sign: Metropolitan Police Public Safety detective Kusakabe Akira}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be the Tomari I've heard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,About me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're somewhat of celebrity in Public Safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who got \NSuperintendent Kirihara locked up, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a bit of a celebrity yourself in the Special Crimes Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You were investigating the murder of Professor Odagiri Masahiko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... that certainly was a bizarre case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a device I had never seen before in the professor's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I found nothing suspicious\Nwhen I checked his computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,His cause of death was recorded\Nas acute cardiac arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what the truth is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But apparently the Professor had an existing heart condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,His heart...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kusakabe, you're with Public Safety...\NWhy were you on this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We were running surveillance on someone that was in contact with Professor Odagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The man you arrested... Nishihori Kouya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the connection between\NNishihori and Professor Odagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell you. You'll have to ask the man himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure how cooperative he'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Having them look into a case from a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This case may have involved Banno...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Banno? You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your collaborator from your human life?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who created the Roidmudes? That Banno?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the late Professor Odagiri's calendar...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Banno's name appeared on it multiple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear me, such a troublesome, tedious, tiring matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Banno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Working on a cold case is rough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of my duty as a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the files, Professor Odagiri had an existing heart condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oda?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If he had a heart attack...\N maybe his medication wasn't effective?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,According to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,His assistant, Kasai, would dissolve his medication in water once a day so that he could drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Heart medication...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard of Professor Odagiri, Saijou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to have some connection to the Special Crimes Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, never heard of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Little lady... why are you looking into that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Otta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to go check on some records, and I heard that someone from Special Crimes had taken the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one in charge of that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would you need the file now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl who went missing last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasai Hitomi has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:58.01,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(233,223)\fs34\bord1.6\shad1.4\4c&H000000&\4a&H00&\pos(640,495)}Ex Criminal Psychologist \N {\fs52\shad3}Nishihori Kouya
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:09:00.89,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{sign: Former Criminologist or whatever we called him, Nishihori Kouya}You must be really stumped if you're here to see me, Tomari Shinnosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cut to the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your relationship with Professor Odagiri Masahiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing complicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was simply curious over some troubling rumors I'd heard about him at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently he made a habit out of plagiarizing his students' research, and taking the credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A similar M.O. to you and your copycat crimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I made contact with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The night before you arrested me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:43.64,Default Top,,0,0,0,,What would a criminologist want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.64,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(485,475)\4a00\fs56\shad3\bord1.6\pos(640,570)}April 7th, 2014 (Monday)  7:02 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was simply curious about your habit of plagiarizing other people's work...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:54.28,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(238,228)\fs30\bord1.6\shad1.4\4c&H000000&\4a00\pos(400,490)}Shinkyo University Human Sciences Dept Professor\N{\fs52\shad3}Odagiri Masahiko
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:55.19,Default Top,,0,0,0,,Plagiarizing...?\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to hide it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've actually been imitating other people's crimes for a while now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you and I share a bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous, I'm nothing like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am doing research that people like you couldn't even fathom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've achieved my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Anima System...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind will be free from the limitation of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am nothing like some common plebeian that mimics others...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You could never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mocking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a busy man. Please, show yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... that's why you killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you mean he's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just punished him a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he was researching...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I increased the voltage on his little invention as high as it would go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:26.04,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(396,438)\4a00\fs56\shad3\bord1.6\pos(640,570)}April 7th, 2014 (Monday)  9:32 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a weak heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I guess I must have killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the time, I still didn't realize...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the truth lurking beneath the surface of this case.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:10.54,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(239,227)\fs34\bord1.6\shad1.4\4c&H000000&\4a&H00&\pos(615,490)}Shinkyo University Human Sciences Dept \N {\fs52\shad3}Kasai Hitomi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.71,Default Top,,0,0,0,,Professor Odagiri died...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two suspects, both claiming to\Nhave committed the crime...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Banno...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ties that bind so many people to this case...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what is the truth?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's the real killer?{\i0}
