Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Anima System he created.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell me how you know Professor Odagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If this case involves the internet, \Nthen the Roidmudes could be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Cores lurk within the internet, absorbing human emotions and spreading across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:30.28,Default Top,,0,0,0,,Keep digging and someone is going to die.
